item.title: Getting started with NetLogo
item.description: NetLogo Setup # NetLogo is available for Windows, Mac, and Linux machines, downloadable from the project homepage. Windows Installer: NetLogo runs on Windows 10, Windows 8, Windows 7 and Vista. NetLogo 5.2.1 was the last version to support Windows XP and Windows 2000. Mac: Mac OS X 10.8.3 or newer is required. (NetLogo 5.1 was the last version to support 10.5 and 10.4; NetLogo 5.2.1 was the last version to support 10.
